            <div class="entry-problem"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;">&lt;보기&gt;를 표현하기 위해 빗댄 대상을 이 글에서 찾아 쓰시오.</p><div class="para0"><table style="border-collapse:collapse;width:260px;margin:3px 3px 3px 3px;" class="itex_example_tb"><tbody><tr><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px solid black; border-collapse:collapse; width:5px; height:8pt"></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="2" style="border:none; border-collapse:collapse; width:70px; height:15pt; vertical-align:middle;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:Center;"><span style="font-size:10pt;">&lt;보기&gt;</span></p></td><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px solid black; border-collapse:collapse; height:8pt"></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px solid black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; height:5pt"></td><td colspan="2" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px solid black;border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; height:5pt"></td></tr><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px solid black;border-right:1px none black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; width:9pt; height:19pt"></td><td colspan="3" rowspan="1" style="border:none; border-collapse:collapse; height:19pt; vertical-align:middle;"><div class="itex_box_body" data-table-title="보기"><p class="para0">눈부시도록 밝게 빛나는 존재</p></div></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px none black;border-right:1px solid black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px none black; border-collapse:collapse; width:9pt; height:19pt"></td></tr><tr><td colspan="5" rowspan="1" style="border-left:1px solid black;border-right:1px solid black;border-top:1px none black;border-bottom:1px solid black; border-collapse:collapse; height:6pt"></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
